text: Prathamesh Parab (born 29 November 1993) is an Indian actor who works primarily in Marathi cinema. Before taking the lead in Timepass, he made his acting debut with Balak Palak. In 2014, he won the Annual Life Ok Screen Awards. == Education == Parab did his schooling at the M.L Dahanukar College of Commerce in Mumbai where he graduated with a Bachelor in Banking and Insurance.
